<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=History_of_Christianity&amp;action=edit&amp;section=93" title="Edit section: Notes">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-2" style="-moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Catechism of the Catholic Church,</li>
<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> Pius XII Mystici corporis Christi</li>
<li id="cite_note-2"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2" title="">^</a></b> Adherents.com, <a href="http://www.adherents.com/Religions_By_Adherents.html" class="external text" title="http://www.adherents.com/Religions_By_Adherents.html" rel="nofollow"><i>Religions by Adherents</i></a></li>
